Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation out of all activity executions in the event log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' out of all cases

Name: Number of times SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation occurs in the entire event log
Percentage of process variants that contain SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation being directly preceded by SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation occurrences that are followed by SW-Awaiting EIC Decision
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' out of all 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Ratio of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation to SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion across all cases
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' out of all 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion'

Name: Number of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation events that occur after at least one instance of SW-Reviewer Agreed in the same case
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' activities for cases where activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' occurs

Name: Percentage of cases where SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation appears but SW-Reviewer Agreed never occurred
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' out of all cases where 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' does not happen

Name: Frequency of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation in variants that ultimately lead to SW-EIC Accept versus those leading to rejection or revision
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' out of all 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Number of process instances where SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation is skipped entirely despite prior SW-Reviewer Agreed events
Metric: Number of 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' activities for cases where activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' does not occur

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation events that occur within 7 days after the last SW-Reviewer Agreed in the same case
Metric: the average of the function base < 604800 where base is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Ratio of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation to SW-AE Assign Reviewers across all completed review cycles
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' out of all 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Frequency of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation appearing in long-running variants (performance > 1,000,000 seconds) compared to short-running ones
Metric: the average of the function base > 1000000 where base is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation that directly follows a sequence containing at least two distinct reviewer responses (e.g., SW-Reviewer Agreed and SW-Reviewer Declined)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation occurrences relative to the total number of reviewer-related activities (e.g., SW-Reviewer Agreed, SW-Reviewer Declined, SW-Reviewer No Response)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' out of all cases
